      "text": "<b>Therefore</b>, teach general concepts first. When teaching details, or other topics that are based on the general topics taught before, this has two positive consequences: The new topic can be remembered more easily, because it can be associated with the general concepts. And the general concepts are stored more thoroughly, because they become <i>[[REPEATED TOPICS]]</i>  as new topics are introduced.\n  ",
